                  <summary><p><title xml:lang="ta">Pākavatam</title>, that is a Tamil prose version of the tenth Skandha of the <title xml:lang="sa">Bhāgavatapurāṇa</title>. Consists in a <foreign xml:lang="sa">pūrvabhāga</foreign> and an <foreign xml:lang="sa">uttarabhāga</foreign>.</p>
